==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: marvel-of-Peru
<hw>marvel-of-Peru</hw></mhw>.
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A common garden plant
(<spn>Mirabilis jalapa</spn> or <spn>Mirabilis uniflora</spn>) of North
America having fragrant red or purple or yellow or white flowers that
open in late afternoon; called also <altname>four-o'clock</altname>. See
<er>four-o'clock</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> common four-o'clock, marvel of Peru, <spn>Mirabilis
jalapa</spn>, <spn>Mirabilis uniflora</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Marvel</ent>⟦br⟧
